inner sanctum acolyte umbra~
an inner sanctum acolyte~
An inner sanctum acolyte tends a ritual circle in the inner passage.
~
Selected from the most capable of the Heartspire's outer servants, inner sanctum acolytes have survived the first trials of the inner rites. They move with the careful precision of those who know exactly what the wrong gesture can summon.
~
