#11209
heartspire inner guard~
a heartspire inner guard~
A heartspire inner guard stands at the inner sanctum approach, spear crossed.
~
The inner guards are chosen for their ability to maintain discipline in proximity to the Heartspire's deeper chambers. They see things on duty that they do not speak of afterward.
~
