umbra revenant heartspire~
an umbra revenant~
An umbra revenant drifts through the inner corridor, trailing shadow substance.
~
A revenant formed from a Heartspire devotee who was consumed by the inner rites before completion. What remains is the ritual purpose without the person.
~
