#11241
void-touched monk umbra~
a void-touched monk~
A void-touched monk moves through the inner passage with ritual deliberateness.
~
A monk of the inner order who has survived direct contact with the Heartspire's void conduit. The contact changed them in ways that are increasingly visible. They do not speak of it but the silence itself speaks.
~
