shadow sentinel heartspire~
a shadow sentinel~
A shadow sentinel stands at the corridor junction, partially merged with the wall.
~
The shadow sentinels are guardians who have been trained to partially dissolve into shadow, making them nearly invisible in the Heartspire's dim interior. The technique has side effects they have learned to live with.
~
