inner vault champion umbra heartspire~
an inner vault champion~
An inner vault champion stands before the vault approach, weapons drawn.
~
Champions assigned to the Heartspire's inner vault are drawn from the most capable of the vanguard and given access to the vault's conditioning rites. They are demonstrably stronger than they were and remember the process with unusual clarity.
~
